{"tid":2034823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］低成本高效益嘅「點燈一小時」","createTime":"2020-05-25T13:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T14:34:14.000Z","uid":121713,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f790b8b20beacad726755a58164d94d710b891","tid":2034823,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"依家班狗同港共咁狼死，唔好話聚人，行出屋企門口已經要拉要鎖，咁樣落去真係等於不斷用手足條命去換全世界已經睇咗一年嘅畫面。<br />\n<br />\n小弟早幾日諗到不如整個低成本又有創意嘅活動爭取國際曝光，就好似上年嘅人鏈咁。<br />\n<br />\n做法就好似左膠活動「地球一小時」咁，揀定一個時間，全世界嘅手足點一個鐘燭光，之後用同一個hashtag post相或者live。呢個活動完全冇風險，又可以超越地域界限，仲可以爭取西方左右兩派一齊支持。<br />\n<br />\n日期可以揀有代表性嘅64 69 612都得，時間小弟就建議香港夜晚十點，倫敦晏晝三點，美國東岸朝早十點，西岸七點。<br />\n<br />\n利申好感激所有行出嚟嘅手足，只不過小弟覺得間唔中加插有創意又可以聚人嘅活動絕對唔係壞事，和勇不分。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n同意請幫推，我哋一齊集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e684cf1d91ac9d8cf93522bc283b6d4987aae078","tid":2034823,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2964b7c4df780a3170e8d1b5306ff8b9e4815c1","tid":2034823,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e1aaec95e2ce17829356d41414d4c9681bf6303","tid":2034823,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d7abaa65ae831fbe805e2fcd67c0c35bf22bbb","tid":2034823,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"try"},{"pid":"80b32ddd0e4b8cb2aa1fe36783bcda4fa15d4b96","tid":2034823,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2026e69e62df47694e37c9294fbe1fd651e261dd","tid":2034823,"uid":186531,"like":0,"disli